---
title: Sweet & Sour Pork with Noodles and Toasted Sesame Seeds
description: Chefs in posh restaurants have been known to eject diners asking for ketchup, but it has its place in plenty of dishes. Today ketchup is our secret ingredient! It brings a delicious sweet and sour note to a sauce for crispy-coated pork and stir-fried veggies and is actually used by lots of Chinese restaurant chefs!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-sour-pork-9c2cfe76-e3ac8b92.jpg
